# SPIMS
## Semester Project Image Matching Software
### CS4500 Software Development - Professor William Clinger
#### Course Website: http://www.ccs.neu.edu/course/cs4500wc/

##### Authors - Emails
 * Brandon Lerner - lernerbrandon@gmail.com
